"""
        Test for parsing mulitple fastas
        """
filename = os.path.join(here, 'test_data/1AY7.pdb.PB.fasta')
headers, sequences = pbx.io.read_fasta(filename)
assert headers == ['test_data/1AY7.pdb | chain A',
    'test_data/1AY7.pdb | chain B']
assert sequences == [
    'ZZbjadfklmcfklmmmmmmmmnnpaafbfkgopacehlnomaccddehjaccdddddehklpnbjadcdddfbehiacddfegolaccdddfkZZ'
    ,
    'ZZcddfklpcbfklmmmmmmmmnopafklgoiaklmmmmmmmmpacddddddehkllmmmmnnommmmmmmmmmmmmmnopacddddZZ'
    ]
